After graduating from Lehigh, New York native Ann Lewnes ’83 reinvented herself on the West Coast with a job at Intel. Then, she went on to reinvent Adobe, Inc., as chief marketing officer and executive vice president of corporate strategy and development. With host Joe Buck, Ann discusses her appetite for risk, her perspectives on up-and-coming talent, and her next big bet on the future of marketing.&nbsp;
